    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the sauce is thickening, cut your<strong> wholemeal pittas</strong> into triangles</p><p>Add the <strong>pitta triangles</strong> to a tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 8-10 min or until crisp and starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 5,
