    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining sliced onion</strong> to a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and mix well</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> leaves from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato </strong>to the bowl with <strong>most</strong> of the <strong>chopped mint</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato & mint salsa</strong></p>",
