    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the<strong> roasted aubergine</strong> with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lean beef mince & aubergine stew</strong></p>",
