    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lean beef mince & aubergine stew</strong> over the <strong>crispy pittas </strong>– this is your <strong>lean beef mince & aubergine fatteh</strong></p><p>Scatter over the <strong>tomato & mint salsa </strong>and crumble your<strong> feta</strong> all over</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
